```plantuml
@startuml vectranetworks_AWS-Traffic-Mirroring-Session-Manager
skinparam sequence {
  LifeLineBorderColor black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #d3d3d3
  ParticipantBorderColor black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
  ActivationBorderColor black
  ActivationBackgroundColor #b0c4de
  ArrowColor #000000
}

actor User

participant "tap.py" as Tap
participant "config_vpc.py" as ConfigVPC
participant "blacklist.py / whitelist.py" as ListManager
participant "ec2_api_client.py" as EC2ApiClient
participant "spile_tapper.py" as SpileTapper
participant "spile.py" as Spile
participant "tag_config.py" as TagConfig
participant "nlb_factory.py" as NlbFactory
participant "nlb_target_factory.py" as NlbTargetFactory

User -> Tap: run
activate Tap

Tap -> ConfigVPC: configure VPC
ConfigVPC -> TagConfig: manage tags
TagConfig --> ConfigVPC: tags managed

Tap -> ListManager: manage instance list
ListManager -> TagConfig: update instance tags
TagConfig --> ListManager: tags updated

Tap -> EC2ApiClient: discover instances
EC2ApiClient --> Tap: instance list

Tap -> SpileTapper: manage sessions
activate SpileTapper
SpileTapper -> Spile: configure session
activate Spile

Spile -> EC2ApiClient: retrieve ENI data
EC2ApiClient --> Spile: ENI data

Spile -> NlbTargetFactory: create mirror target
NlbTargetFactory --> Spile: target created

Spile -> NlbFactory: create NLB
NlbFactory --> Spile: NLB created

Spile --> SpileTapper: session configured
deactivate Spile

SpileTapper --> Tap: sessions managed
deactivate SpileTapper

deactivate Tap

@enduml
```